{"tid":2368732,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地增115宗本土個案　北京佔兩病例","createTime":"2021-01-16T12:31:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T12:32:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c3e718678c7cdcf9c9e3f7217f7c9fdfc82e3e","tid":2368732,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:31:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570724-20210116.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570724-20210116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyAKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=2fff9946\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570724-20210116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2a1e7b5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570724-20210116.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n內地過去一日新增130宗新型肺炎確診個案，當中115宗是本土感染病例，數字連續四日破百。本土個案中，河北佔90宗、黑龍江23宗、北京兩宗，令內地現時一共有88118人染病，單日無新增患者不治個案，死亡人數維持在4635人。<br />\n<br />\n另外，內地單日新增79宗無症狀感染者，20人當日轉為確診。"},{"pid":"70ecf5151942700e982f45a79ada9cdc520eea26","tid":2368732,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:32:23.000Z","msg":"真實數字應該乘一萬"},{"pid":"21c0ec7426fccc77793c812ad1e91eca28898c72","tid":2368732,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:32:40.000Z","msg":"rthk 已犯國安法<br />\n我大中國會有人感染？<br />\n拉！"}]}